Author: livipup
Text: I go through periods where I don't feel hungry at all followed by periods where I never stop feeling hungry. I have to force myself to eat when I'm not hungry so I can be healthy and then I have to restrain myself when I'm endlessly hungry to keep myself from eating until I get sick. It's a pretty terrible cycle. Especially since it doesn't take much to make me sick ðŸ˜ª
